### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@customerToken = YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@painterToken = YOUR_PAINTER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Request Booking (Customer only) - Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-request
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2025-10-15T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-15T12:00:00Z"
}

### Request Another Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-request
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2025-10-15T13:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-15T15:00:00Z"
}

### Request Booking - No Painter Available (get recommendations)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-request
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2025-10-20T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-20T12:00:00Z"
}

### Get My Bookings (Customer only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/me
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Get Assigned Bookings (Painter only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/assigned
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

